{"tid":689623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"偷人銀包留返證件大行動","createTime":"2018-06-04T08:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T10:27:02.000Z","uid":184220,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ee1dc6567ac68fa754cc16946ef99b5316f58d","tid":689623,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"君子莫大乎與人為善<br />\n我決定舉辦慈善活動<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 偷人銀包留返證件大行動</span></strong></div><br />\n好心偷銀包偷銀包 比返啲證件人<br />\n整返好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正所謂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">凡事留一線 日後好相見<br />\n盜亦有道<br />\n人之初 性本善<br />\n善人者 人亦善之<br />\n竊錢袋者 應返之證件<br />\n苦海無邊 回頭是戇<br />\n天不可無日月 人不可無善德</span><br />\n<br />\n反正證件對你冇用 不如放係當眼位置<br />\n等人執返都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">比返啲錢都好 唔舉報你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"22e32fc14ffb2b7434d633859fd5e0ea76c32181","tid":689623,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"你講得好正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c241f2e5ecc08cd4ac763d25a709fa355df53e","tid":689623,"uid":26971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22e32fc14ffb2b7434d633859fd5e0ea76c32181","tid":689623,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"你講得好正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5605a2462b31ee8c8ab8b405f5b9a1f993cb820","tid":689623,"uid":184220,"like":0,"disl